-- Russian January Services PMI Growth Accelerates to 6-Month High
-- B y   S c o t t   R o s e
-- 2012-02-03T05:04:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-03/russian-january-services-pmi-growth-accelerates-to-6-month-high.html
Russian services-industry growth
reached a six-month high in January as new business accelerated
and unemployment declined, HSBC Holdings Plc said.  The HSBC Russia Services PMI grew to 56.5 from 53.8 in
December for a 17th month of gains, the U.K. bank said in a
report today, citing data compiled by  Markit Economics . A
reading above 50 shows growth, below 50 contraction. The measure
reached 56.9 in July.  To contact the reporter on this story:
